    "body": "It seems no, currentState does not include the pending txs and contains a state of the blockchain head .\r\n\r\n```\r\n\tcurrentState  *state.StateDB      // Current state in the blockchain head\r\n\tpendingState  *state.ManagedState // Pending state tracking virtual nonces\r\n```\r\n\r\nI also have made some tests on a private network to be sure. You can send a lot of txs without getting \"ErrInsufficientFunds\".",
